---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Anthropic Claude Models - Evvl" description="Compare and evaluate Anthropic's Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Claude 3 Opus, and other Claude models with Evvl.">
  <Nav />

  <article class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-muted hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-8">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
        </svg>
        Back to Home
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <img src="/logos/dark/claude.svg" alt="" class="h-12 logo-dark" />
        <img src="/logos/light/claude.svg" alt="" class="h-12 logo-light" />
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary">Anthropic</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted mb-12">Evaluate Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Claude 3 Opus, and other Claude models side by side.</p>

      <!-- Key Models -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Available Models</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bento-card p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Claude 3.5 Sonnet</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">The sweet spot of intelligence and speed. Excellent for coding and analysis.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 text-xs">Best Value</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-xs">200K Context</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-card p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Claude 3 Opus</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Most capable Claude model. Best for complex, nuanced tasks requiring deep understanding.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 text-xs">Most Capable</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-xs">200K Context</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-card p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Claude 3.5 Haiku</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Fast and affordable. Great for high-volume tasks and quick responses.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 text-xs">Fastest</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 text-xs">Cost-Effective</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bento-card p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Claude 3 Sonnet</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Previous generation balanced model. Still excellent for many use cases.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-gray-500/10 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-xs">Balanced</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-xs">200K Context</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Best For -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Best For</h2>
        <div class="bento-card p-8">
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-primary">Long-form writing</strong> — Excellent prose quality and consistency</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-primary">Code review and generation</strong> — 3.5 Sonnet rivals specialized coding models</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-primary">Analysis and research</strong> — Strong at synthesizing information from large contexts</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong class="text-primary">Instruction following</strong> — Reliably follows complex, multi-step instructions</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Integration -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">Using Claude with Evvl</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>To use Claude models in Evvl, you'll need an API key from <a href="https://console.anthropic.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent hover:underline">console.anthropic.com</a>.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-primary">Web App:</strong> Anthropic calls are proxied through our servers due to CORS restrictions. Your API key is never stored—it's only used for the request and immediately discarded.</p>
          <p><strong class="text-primary">Desktop App:</strong> All calls go directly to Anthropic's API with no intermediary.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="bento-card p-8 text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-accent)]/10 to-transparent !border-[var(--color-accent)]/20">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Start comparing Claude models</h3>
        <p class="text-muted mb-6">See how Claude 3.5 Sonnet compares to Opus, GPT-4o, and Gemini.</p>
        <a href="https://app.evvl.ai" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Try Evvl Free
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
